title: OpenVPN+Alonweb
description:
Taste the freedom of the Internet!

Ever faced the problem of blocking of your favourite websites at your corporate firewall? Don't want your boss, admin or local Big Brother to see what sites you visit, what you speak about on your favourite IM or what e-mails you send? There's only one solution for these problems: using crypted VPN tunnel to bypass your internet access resticitions and to secure sensitive information you transfer on the Net. Alonweb provides the Internet community with stable and reliable OpenVPN service free of charge.
